@cindex @code{compile-only}
@kindex compile-only
@format
@code{compile-only} ( @i{--  }) gforth-0.2 ``compile-only''
@end format
Mark the last definition as compile-only; as a result, the text interpreter
and @code{'} will warn when they encounter such a word.


